import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
import scipy
import itables.interactive
from itables import show
#from IPython.display import HTML, display
#import tabulate

df_PIX=pd.read_csv("..\data\PIX_data_article_20200630.csv", encoding='utf-8', sep=",")
df_AIX=pd.read_csv("..\data\AIX_data_article_20200630.csv", encoding='utf-8', sep=",")

#df_PIX

#show(df_PIX)

df_PIX['Minuten']=df_PIX['ZeitintervallPIX']/60
df_PIX['Stunden']=df_PIX['Minuten']/60
df_AIX['Minuten']=df_AIX['Zeitintervall']/60
df_AIX['Stunden']=df_AIX['Minuten']/60

df_P=df_PIX[['ArticleId', 'MaxPublishDate','Title', 'Heading','WordCount','IndexGesamtPIX', 'LesedauerPIX', 'IndexRWPIX',
       'IndexLDPIX', 'ZeitintervallPIX', 'Minuten', 'Stunden',  '_Version',
       'Style', 'Channel', 'Subchannel', 'isPlus']].round(1)

df_P['_Version']=pd.to_datetime(df_P['_Version'])
df_P['MaxPublishDate']=pd.to_datetime(df_P['MaxPublishDate'])

#df_P.columns

idx = df_P.groupby(['ArticleId', 'MaxPublishDate','Stunden'])['_Version'].transform(max) == df_P['_Version']
dfPIX=df_P[idx][['ArticleId', 'MaxPublishDate', 'Title', 'WordCount',
       'IndexGesamtPIX','IndexLDPIX', 'IndexRWPIX',  'Stunden', 'Style',
       'Channel', 'Subchannel', 'isPlus']].rename(columns={"MaxPublishDate": "PublishDate","IndexGesamtPIX": "IndexPIX"}, errors="raise")

def print_articles_published(min_PublishDate, 
                             max_PublishDate,
                             column=['IndexPIX', 'IndexLDPIX', 'IndexRWPIX'], 
                             minimum=(0,100, 1), 
                             maximum=(0,100, 1)):
    
    min_PublishDate = pd.to_datetime(min_PublishDate)
    max_PublishDate = pd.to_datetime(max_PublishDate)
    #return df_PIX_display.loc[(df_PIX_display[column] > minimum) & (df_PIX_display[column] < maximum)]
    return show(df.loc[(df.index >= min_PublishDate) 
                  & (df.index <= max_PublishDate)
                  &((df[column]) > minimum) 
                  & ((df[column]) < maximum)].sort_values(column), maxBytes=0)

#pd.to_datetime('2020-03-11')

Timestamp('2020-03-11 00:00:00')
_ = interact(print_articles_published,
             min_PublishDate=widgets.DatePicker(value=pd.to_datetime('2020-03-11')),
             max_PublishDate=widgets.DatePicker(value=pd.to_datetime('2021-01-01')))
